sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Visitor
    participant NewsletterUI as Lab Newsletter Component
    participant Validation as Zod Email Schema
    participant SubsAPI as POST /api/subscribers
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant Dashboard as Subscribers Dashboard

    Visitor->>NewsletterUI: Enter email and submit
    NewsletterUI->>Validation: Validate email format

    alt Invalid email
        Validation-->>NewsletterUI: Error
        NewsletterUI-->>Visitor: Show validation message
    else Valid email
        NewsletterUI->>SubsAPI: Submit email + source
        SubsAPI->>DB: Upsert SUBSCRIBER by email

        alt Existing subscriber
            DB-->>SubsAPI: Existing row updated
            SubsAPI-->>NewsletterUI: 200 OK (already subscribed)
        else New subscriber
            DB-->>SubsAPI: New row created
            SubsAPI-->>NewsletterUI: 201 Created
        end

        NewsletterUI-->>Visitor: Show subscription confirmation
        Dashboard->>SubsAPI: GET /api/subscribers
        SubsAPI->>DB: Read subscriber table
        DB-->>SubsAPI: Subscriber rows
        SubsAPI-->>Dashboard: Render subscribers list
    end
